longBusinessSummary: DEFAMA Deutsche Fachmarkt AG, a real estate company, engages in the purchase and long-term rental of retail parks and shopping centers. The company focuses on small commercial properties in small and medium-sized cities primarily in northern and eastern Germany. DEFAMA Deutsche Fachmarkt AG was founded in 2014 and is based in Berlin, Germany.
